{"lexicon" 1, "id" "com.etzhayyim.maps.ownership", "description" "Ownership relation event — a LegalEntity (subject) owns/transfers/inherits/forecloses/leases a registry record (object). Append-only event log keyed by TID; chain of ownership reconstructed by reading by `subjectUri` or `objectUri` + sorting by `effectiveDate`. Per maps CLAUDE.md §Registry & Legal Entity Architecture (`edge_ownership`) + ADR-2605231400 kotoba-datomic L1.", "defs" {"main" {"type" "record", "key" "tid", "record" {"type" "object", "required" ["v" "subjectUri" "objectUri" "relation" "effectiveDate"], "properties" {"supersededByUri" {"type" "string", "format" "at-uri", "description" "If a later record corrects this one (rare), point to the replacement. The original remains queryable for audit."}, "registryRef" {"type" "string", "description" "Free-form reference to the source filing (e.g., 'JP-MOJ 13-01234 行 5').", "maxLength" 256}, "effectiveDate" {"type" "string", "format" "datetime"}, "sharePctBps" {"type" "integer", "description" "Ownership share in basis points (10000 = 100%). Integer to avoid float drift.", "minimum" 0, "maximum" 10000}, "v" {"type" "integer", "minimum" 1, "maximum" 1}, "objectUri" {"type" "string", "format" "at-uri", "description" "AT URI of the Registry record being owned / transferred / inherited / leased."}, "sourceDid" {"type" "string", "format" "did"}, "subjectUri" {"type" "string", "format" "at-uri", "description" "AT URI of the LegalEntity acting as owner / transferor / lessee."}, "relation" {"type" "string", "knownValues" ["OwnsProperty" "TransferredTo" "InheritedBy" "ForeclosedBy" "LeasedTo"]}}}}}}